quran[14{c,v,t}:
43,34,Wa libu yootihim abwaabanw wa sururan 'alaihaa yattaki'oon
43,35,Wa zukhrufaa; wa in kullu zaalika lammaa mataa'ul hayaatid dunyaa; wal aakhiratu 'inda Rabbika lilmuttaqeen�(section 3)
43,36,Wa mai ya'shu 'an zikrir Rahmaani nuqaiyid lahoo Shaitaanan fahuwa lahoo qareen
43,37,Wa innahum la yasuddoo nahum 'anis sabeeli wa yahsaboona annahum muhtadoon
43,38,Hattaaa izaa jaaa'anaa qaala yaa laita bainee wa bainaka bu'dal mashriqaini fabi'sal qareen
43,39,Wa lai yanfa'akumul Yawma iz zalamtum annakum fil 'azaabi mushtarikoon
43,40,Afa anta tusmi'us summa aw tahdil 'umya wa man kaana fee dalaalim mubeen
43,41,Fa immaa nazhabanna bika fa innaa minhum muntaqimoon
43,42,Aw nuriyannakal lazee wa'adnaahum fa innaa 'alaihim muqtadiroon
43,43,Fastamsik billazeee oohi ya ilaika innaka 'alaa Siraatim Mustaqeem
43,44,Wa innahoo lazikrul laka wa liqawmika wa sawfa tus'aloon
43,45,Was'al man arsalnaa min qablika mir Rusulinaaa aja'alnaa min doonir Rahmaani aalihatany yu badoon�(section 4)
43,46,Wa laqad arsalnaa Moosaa bi aayaatinaaa ilaa Fir'awna wa mala'ihee faqaala innee Rasoolu Rabbil 'aalameen
43,47,Falammma jaaa'ahum bi aayaatinaaa izaa hum minhaa yadhakoon
